  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> It is the value of the facet?\r\n\r\nIn your example, the value of `imageDescription` each record.\r\nHowever that would involve passing each record through this function, which I'm sure is not what would be happening.\r\n\r\n...So maybe a function doesn't make sense.\r\n\r\nInitially I was thinking an array, because it felt similar to how you would pass a [FacetList](https://community.algolia.com/algoliasearch-helper-js/reference.html#SearchParameters.FacetList) to `SearchParameters.disjunctiveFacetsRefinements`.",
